<div class="panel">
<p>Under the supervision and direction of qualified nursing staff, healthcare assistants carry out a wide range of duties to care for, support, and provide information to patients and their families. They also look after the physical comfort of patients, for example, helping them to wash and emptying bedpans.</p>
